                        <li>Rock <span class="right label label-danger">16.9%</span></li>
                        <li>Pop <span class="right label label-success">15.5%</span></li>
                        <li>Pagode <span class="right label label-primary">11.8%</span></li>
                        <li>Religious <span class="right label label-danger">3.2%</span></li>
                        <li>Instrumentals <span class="right label label-warning">3%</span></li>
                        <li>Movies Soundtrack <span class="right label label-warning">0%</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-5">
            <div class="panel panel-widget" style="height:450px;">
                <div class="panel-title">
                    Some of my Favorites <span class="glyphicon glyphicons-heart"></span>
